short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Anti-phishing browser extension. Scan suspicious pages and links.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: PhishDetect is a browser extension designed to protect you from phishing attacks. Using the menu you are able to request a link or the content of a visited page to be analyzed by our PhishDetect service and determine if it's suspicious.
